                            <comment id="18004745" author="erans" created="Fri, 11 Jul 2025 16:58:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you suggest that we throw &lt;tt&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/tt&gt; (because clustering wouldn&apos;t make sense for this dataset) instead?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18004841" author="JIRAUSER310071" created="Sat, 12 Jul 2025 09:49:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for the feedback! I agree that throwing an &lt;tt&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/tt&gt; is a good approach to handle this case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18004904" author="erans" created="Sat, 12 Jul 2025 23:02:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In commit 1e59551f3083cc40c510094e4fce13f19de52e16 (&quot;master&quot; branch), the precondition is enforced by checking that &lt;tt&gt;sumSqDist&lt;/tt&gt; is not zero (otherwise, IAE is thrown).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
